    "This is particularly valuable for non-destructive testing, where flawed specimens can be identified in terms of anomalies.",
    "The approach relies on generative models and attempts to reconstruct the geometry.",
    "At first, the generative model is trained on structures without flaws.",
    "During evaluation, the structures to be tested are then fed through the NN.",
    "In case of an autoencoder, as in [589], it is fed through the encoder and decoder."
